E04       |    DAVID       |    SALES   |    55000     |    40
E05       |    MARK        |    SALES   |    60000     |    45
E06       |    JOE         |    SALES   |    40000     |    25
E07       |    BELLA       |    HR      |    60000     |    24

h4:FilterByNumberRange Node Configuration

FilterByNumberRange node is configured as below:

INPUT COLUMN NAME    :    AGE
LOWEST VALUE         :    35
HIGHEST VALUE        :    45

